                              framework has a method..." <BR>Page 303 =
says=20
                              Observer appears in MVC for the first =
time, and=20
                              from there we can't deduce MVC is a =
pattern.<BR>
                              &nbsp;<BR>AFAIK the Design Patterns book =
is one of=20
                              the main references of the terminology. =
I'm not=20
                              saying is the best or so, but they're one =
of the=20
                              first who used the term in a strong =
context like a=20
                              book.<BR>&nbsp;<BR>If you find another =
quite far=20
                              source, I would very glad to see it. =
