                              really appreciate to read people which is=20
                              well-ackowledged in computer science and =
not from=20
                              John Doe MVP of Micro/Sun/HP and three "MS =

                              approved" "papers".<BR>&nbsp;<BR>Some good =
and=20
                              correct clarification I've found browsing =
the=20
                              web:<BR>&nbsp;<BR>A framework is a =
reusable,=20
                              ``semi-complete'' application that can be=20
                              specialized to produce custom applications =
as=20
                              described by Ralph Johnson and Brian =
Foote. <BR>
                              &nbsp;<BR>As the definition says, a frame =
work is=20
                              a semi complete Application .For eg Struts =

                              Framework is used as a base for many =
custom=20
                              applications <BR>&nbsp;<BR>A Design =
pattern is not=20
                              an application but is a solution to a =
commonly=20
                              occuring design problem. We can use a =
Pattern to=20
                              avoid some of the possible design draw =
backs in=20
                              the application being designed. These =
patterns can=20
                              be used by all applications( including =
frameworks=20
                              to make the application robust =
)<BR>&nbsp;<BR>To=20
                              have millions of humans thinking the earth =
is like=20
                              a square has proved them to be right?<BR>
                              &nbsp;<BR>Regards<BR><BR></TD></TR>
